'''Lord Protector of Aquilae''' was a title granted to [[Annikin Starkiller]] by his lover, the new [[Queen/Legends|Queen]] [[Leia (The Star Wars)|Leia]] of [[Aquilae (The Star Wars)|Aquilae]] following the destruction of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Death Star/Legends|space fortress]].

